3-Xu%C3%A2n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-PBy92bBuBMMs53v9tc9E0A">Hồ Xuân Hương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Qu%C3%A1t/Th%C6%B0-ho%C3%A0i-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-Rptw3XTP4lNbn70FmYDuLA">Thư hoài kỳ 2 - 書懷其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Qu%C3%A1t/author-QI5swJgvY3VYWMQRAtFosg">Lê Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C6%B0/poem-WQkvak0bO6BDMarTsB2kng">Trường tương tư - 長相思</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/author-Rh6zapU4AwLAuhG1Xl_FMw">Âu Dương Tu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C5%A9-k%E1%BB%B3-3-V%E1%BA%ADt-s%E1%BA%AFc-tu%E1%BA%BF-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-y%E1%BA%BFn/poem-6d-tSp5Lihmwp033ypKNMA">Vũ kỳ 3 (Vật sắc tuế tương yến) - 雨其三（物色歲將晏）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C4%90oan/Vu-s%C6%A1n-cao/poem-nkLK983trvV6S_1lIDQRkA">Vu sơn cao - 巫山高</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C4%90oan/author-vHSGJ24Oq83oesxet8BFJA">Lý Đoan</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
